==============================================
== Installation Instructions
==============================================

to Compile the program go into folder Release and type :
	make clean
	make -j

=================
== Dependencies
=================

For graphical output:
 - R + grid package => install it

For XXmasker:
- formatdb, blast => install blast2


================================================
== FAQ:
================================================

1.) compilation error stl_list.h:

	 probably you are using g++ version 4.2, which has a bug in allocator.h:
		
			install libstdc++6-4.X-dev, X > 2
